<div style="padding: 0.2em 0; line-height: 1.3em;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><a href="/wiki/Jewish%E2%80%93Roman_wars" title="Jewish–Roman wars">Jewish–Roman wars</a></span></div>
</th>
